title: clown monster
description: low poly monster model for extras in your game
longDescription: The model is made according to the identical dimensions of the mannequin (all the joints of the shoulder, finger and others have the same size as the mannequin), which allows you to use all the standard animations without any distortion. It has 3 sets of unique textures
